## 3. Risk Assessment Summary

### Shadow AI Risk

{% if shadow_ai_controls %}
Technical and/or policy controls are in place to detect unapproved AI usage. This is a **managed risk**.
{% else %}
{% if shadow_ai_aware %}
Management is **aware** that employees are using unapproved AI tools but **no controls are in place**. This is a **high, unmanaged risk**.
{% else %}
Management has **not assessed** whether employees are using unapproved AI tools. Given industry research showing 80% shadow AI adoption, this is a **critical blind spot**.
{% endif %}

**Recommended Actions:**
- Deploy DNS-level blocking of unapproved AI services
- Conduct anonymous staff survey on AI tool usage
- Implement network monitoring for AI service traffic
{% endif %}

